trans-unit.target: Specifica un tipo di intervallo.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType> enumeration represents date and time interval types.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>enumerazione rappresenta i tipi di intervallo di date e time.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>

trans-unit.source: Note that if you use the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType> value, properties other than IntervalType or IntervalOffsetType will treat <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType> as an <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType> value.
trans-unit.target: Si noti che se si utilizza il <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>valore della proprietà diverse da IntervalType o IntervalOffsetType considereranno <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>come un <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>valore.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType> values are applicable to the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelStyle>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.TickMark> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> classes.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>sono applicabili a valori di <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelStyle>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.TickMark>e <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>classi.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.TickMark> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelStyle> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>
